<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">

<html xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_3.xsd" xmlns:p="tapestry:parameter">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="${context:css/examples/examples.css}"/>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Add Person</h1>

The form generated by <strong>Tapestry 5 - Spring 5 Integration</strong> will send its contents in an HTTP POST.<br/><br/>

<div class="eg">
    <t:form t:id="personForm">
        <t:errors/>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td>Name:</td>
                <td><t:textfield t:id="name"/></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Country:</td>
                <td><t:textfield t:id="country"/></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td></td>
                <td><input type="submit" value="Save"/></td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </t:form>
</div>

<div class="eg">
<table t:type="grid" t:source="persons" t:row="person" t:model="mymodel" t:rowsPerPage="4" t:pagerPosition="top">
    <p:actionCell>
        <a t:type="eventLink" t:event="Delete" t:context="[person.id]">Delete</a>
    </p:actionCell>
</table>
</div>
</body>
</html>
